# Virtual Piano

## Summary
The `VirtualPiano` card provides a fully interactive virtual piano experience, allowing users to play, record, and explore music using the VP.net notation system.

## Import
```javascript
import { VirtualPiano } from '../virtual-piano';
```

## Usage as a Field
The `VirtualPiano` card can be used as a field within a consuming card or field. Here's an example:

```javascript
import { CardDef, field, contains } from 'https://cardstack.com/base/card-api';
import { VirtualPiano } from '../virtual-piano';

class MyCard extends CardDef {
  @field piano = contains(VirtualPiano);
}
```

## Template Usage
To use the `VirtualPiano` card in a template, simply include the component:

```html
<VirtualPiano @model={{this.piano}} />
```

This will render the full interactive virtual piano experience within the consuming card or field.
